body_html: I had the same problem. Tensorflow wants at least two categories. After that, I still had an issue and realized that my second folder only contained PNG files. I exported one of the PNG files as a Jpeg and the problem was solved. So in short, it needs at least two folders and it seems to be partial to Jpeg files.
